  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading",
          "anchor": "Overview",
          "level": 2
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Use app intents to express your app’s capabilities to the system. An app intent",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "text": "includes the code you need to perform an action, and expresses the data you",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "text": "require from the system. The system exposes your actions directly from the",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Shortcuts app and in system experiences like Siri."
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "To define an action, create a type that adopts the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.AppIntents/documentation/AppIntents/AppIntent",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " protocol,",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "or a related protocol that provides the specific behavior you need. Annotate",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "text": "any key properties with the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "@Parameter"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " property wrapper to let the system"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "know you need the associated information to perform the action."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The system uses intent attributes like ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference",
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.AppIntents/documentation/AppIntents/AppIntent/title"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " and "
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.AppIntents/documentation/AppIntents/AppIntent/description",
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true
            },
            {
              "text": " to inform people about your intent’s functionality in the Shortcuts app. Supplement this information with ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.AppIntents/documentation/AppIntents/IntentDescription",
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " metadata, and provide additional context through human-readable explanations of your intent’s functionality, including category information and search keywords. This metadata helps your intents appear in interfaces like the Shortcuts app and improves their discoverability."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "For more information about features App Intents enables, see "
            },
            {
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference",
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.AppIntents/documentation/AppIntents/Making-actions-and-content-discoverable-and-widely-available"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
